#: src/window/main_window.rs
msgid ""
"This will remove all stopped containers, dangling images, and unused "
"networks. This cannot be undone."
msgstr ""
"Hii itaondoa kontena zote zilizosimamishwa, picha zinazoning'inia, na "
"mitandao isiyotumika. Hii haiwezi kutenduliwa."

